          <title>Golden State Valkyries unveil season games, home opener</title>
          <description><![CDATA[(KRON) – The newest Bay Area major pro sports team, the Golden State Valkyries, has announced the date of its inaugural season at the Chase Center on Monday.  The inaugural game, slated for May 16 of next year, will be a California battle with the Valkyries facing the Los Angeles Sparks.]]></description>
